1 that do not require the child to share a room or sleeping quarters with an individual of the opposite sex.
2 (3) A parent must be notified of the right to opt out of any physical and mental health surveys and
3 screenings of their child. A parent must be notified of any issues or concerns resulting from a physical and
4 mental health survey or screening of their child.
